snippet.title: CAMELS / FERRETS / WHALES - You have NO IDEA HOW FUNNY they are!
snippet.description:
Did you know that ferrets, whales and camels can be so funny? This videos are so funny and I bet that you will laugh your head off! The hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look how all these animals behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
